What is *planning problem ?*

A planning problem is to *Optimise goals with limited resources under constraints*

*Optimise goals*: Maximise profit, Minimise ecological footprint, Maximize happiness of employees/customers

*with limited resources* :Employees Assest( machines ,buildings,Vehicles 
Time,Budget)

*under constraints* : employees vs Workin hours employee vs skills/affinity
assest vs/Logistic conflicts

ifdef::showscript[]
[.notes]
***
Planner is a constraint satisfaction solver. It optimizes business resource planning. Every organization faces scheduling puzzles: assign a limited set of constrained resources (employees, assets, time and money) to provide products or services to customers. Planner optimizes such planning problems to do more business with less resources

****
endif::showscript[]